
## Create VxLAN Connection

## Enter System View
system-view

## Create bridge domain
bridge-domain  ${Bd_Id}
vxlan vni ${Vni}
quit

## Create Vbd Interface
interface Vbdif${Bd_Id}
ip address 10.10.10.1 255.255.255.0
quit

## Config Nve Interface
interface Nve 1
source ${LocalAddress}
vni ${Vni} head-end peer-list ${PeerAddress}
quit

## Exit System View
quit
